place_info.title: クリニックフォア池袋
place_info.address: Japan, 〒171-0022 Tokyo, Toshima City, Minamiikebukuro, 1 Chome−27−10 油木第１ビル 2F

reviews.snippet:
Klinik pertama yang ku jejaki di jepun dan kebetulan berada di kawasan ikebukuro. Went here because of the rating star in google. Communicate with the staff and doctor using google translate. My symptom; sore throat, running nose with mucus. Required to fill up registration form and they provide a thermometer for you to measure body temperature (place under your armpit). Was told waiting period around 30min - 1 hour. Klinik konsultasi berada di tingkat 2 manakala farmasi ubat di tingkat 1. Jumpa doktor wanita, sesi tanya jawab, dia cadangkan untuk buat pemeriksaan covid-19. Lepas selesai, aku pun bayar lah ¥12,650 (the receipt from POS machine shows ¥10,000 however another printed receipt from PC [maybe] shows ¥12,650, I’m confused). Disuruh ke tingkat bawah untuk ambil ubat. Dapatlah 3 jenis ubat. Ingatkan kos konsultasi tadi termasuk ubat rupa-rupanya tidak. Kos ubat sahaja ¥15,720. Jadi, jumlah perbelanjaan ¥28,370. Bayar guna kad kredit. Dorang siap bagi buku kecil
Nota Perubatan. Jadi begitulah kisahnya.
reviews.translated_snippet:
The first clinic I visited in Japan and it happened to be in the Ikebukuro area. Went here because of the star rating in google. Communicated with the staff and doctor using google translate. My symptom; sore throat, running nose with mucus. Required to fill up a registration form and they provide a thermometer for you to measure body temperature (place under your armpit). Was told waiting period around 30min - 1 hour. The consultation clinic was on the 2nd floor while the pharmacy was on the 1st floor. Met a female doctor, had a question and answer session, she suggested a covid-19 checkup. After that, I paid ¥12,650 (the receipt from POS machine shows ¥10,000 however another printed receipt from PC [maybe] shows ¥12,650, I’m confused). Was told to go downstairs to get medicine. Got 3 types of medicine. Remember the consultation cost included medicine which apparently didn’t. The medicine cost alone was ¥15,720. So, total expense ¥28,370. Pay with a credit card. They're ready to give you a little book
Medical Notes. So that's the story.

place_info.title: Pro Wheel Tyre Auto Service Sdn. Bhd.
place_info.address: 20, Jalan Tiara 5, Bandar Baru Klang, 41150 Klang, Selangor, Malaysia

reviews.snippet:
Harga tayar antara termurah di pasaran.
Beroperasi di dalam shopee dengan nama @onlinetyreshop

Pembayaran melalui e-wallet / online transfer tiada caj tambahan. Sekiranya menggunakan kad kredit atau debit, CAJ TAMBAHAN sebanyak 2.8% akan dikenakan.

Layanan kurang memuaskan dan rata-rata pekerja tidak mesra pelanggan. Servis pelanggan tidak memuaskan dan perlu diperbaiki.

Alignment akan dikenakan caj sebanyak RM30
Sewaktu proses alignment, pekerja akan menyarankan untuk memperbetulkan chamber dimana ianya akan dikenakan caj tambahan (saya tak buat)
Tyre valve biasa berharga RM5 / sebiji tayar. Sekiranya anda tidak menukar valve baru mereka tidak akan bagi jaminan (warranty)

Kesimpulannya, harga tayar yang ditawarkan murah TETAPI mereka akan menyarankan anda untuk menambah itu ini bagi mengaut wang dari poket anda.
reviews.translated_snippet:
Tire prices are among the cheapest in the market.
Operates in shopee under the name @onlinetyreshop

Payment via e-wallet / online transfer has no additional charges. If using a credit or debit card, an ADDITIONAL CHARGES of 2.8% will be charged.

The service is less than satisfactory and the average employee is not customer friendly. Customer service is not satisfactory and needs to be improved.

Alignment will be charged RM30
During the alignment process, the employee will recommend correcting the chamber which will incur an additional charge (I did not do it)
Tyre valves usually cost RM5 / tire. If you do not change the new valve they will not provide a warranty

In conclusion, the tire price offered is cheap BUT they will recommend you to add this and that to take money from your pocket.

place_info.title: The +OB•Gynae @ Subang Jaya| Dr Sharad Ratna
place_info.address: Unit 6, UOA Business Park, 51a, Jalan Pengaturcara, Kawasan Perindustrian Temasya, 40150 Shah Alam, Selangor, Malaysia

reviews.snippet:
Selected this place because of the 4 star rating. From my visit in July 2023 for ultrasound scanning:

1. was charged RM360 instead of RM350 as said during tele-conversation. Payment mode is CASH only, what a joke! it’s 2023!
2. the clinic ambient felt “dead” and not lively
3. they’ll charge RM20 if you make the toilet wet, they put a note on the wall (the toilet was wet when i entered, not sure if someone has been penalised)
4. Dr. Sharad & nurse/receptionist were SEEM friendly but, felt FAKE. Not genuine
5. Dr. Sharad was acting defensive towards my question. He should has explain the info 1 by 1 thoroughly. Being a specialist with numbers of certificates but act like operator.
6. They don’t even have weight & height scale to measure, what a joke? since they need the info they should have one!
7. Dr Sharad dont even wear glove during check-up. The gel wasn’t apply properly!
8. The quality of paper of the scanning result is worst for RM350. compared to RM180 i paid at other clinic which was very clear.
9. No proper printed receipt, they used cheap receipt book from stationary.

In a nutshell, I would not recommend this place. Don’t trust the 4-star rating.. honest review.

response.snippet:
Our prices are competitive and varies on the complexity of the consultation.

We like our clinic toilet clean and dry.

Stop psychoanalysing medical professionals and reviewing above your class as there are are many wannabe influencer types around.
I suggest you stick to food reviews as 18/22 reviews are on how your budget 'street food' taste buds(such as mamak roti canai) can be stimulated and your hunger pangs satisfied cheaply.
Maybe Honda is not listening to you... Talk to your Customer Service with suggestions for service improvement within Honda first before expanding to other industries

Let the medical professionals do their jobs well.
